      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The chief interest in the Tacoma\n\n\n1t is this pernicious political &C\ntivity of the whisky men that is\ndriving some of the best and most\nliberal minded people TO prohibition.\nIf to take a glass of beer a patron\nmust permit the saloonkeeper to\nrun the politics of the city, the state\nand the nation, the man will do\nwithout the beer rather than stand\nthe domination of the man in the\nliquor business. This activity Of\nthe liquor people is what will force\nthe county unit Of local option in\nthe state of Washington and else\nwhere. The liquor people do not\nseem to realize this. but are intent\non bling masters of the roost, no\nmatter what the cost."
    }
